Konstantin Koltsov
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







Q. Tell me what makes you most excited about what happened today.

INTERPRETER: The team that has chosen him. 

Q. Do you have a favorite player who is on the Penguins? 

INTERPRETER: Mario Lemieux.

Q. Do you think you're ready to play this season or do you need more time?

INTERPRETER: He thinks he needs a little bit more time.

Q. Who is the first person you're going to call on the telephone to tell the news?

KONSTANTIN KOLTSOV: Mother. 

Q. Where is she?

KONSTANTIN KOLTSOV: From Minsk.

